# Grafbase Provider

The Grafbase provider allows you to manage Grafbase resources such as graphs and branches through Terraform.

## Example Usage

```terraform
terraform {
  required_providers {
    grafbase = {
      source = "grafbase/grafbase"
    }
  }
}

provider "grafbase" {
  api_key = var.grafbase_api_key
}

resource "grafbase_graph" "example" {
  account_slug = "my-account"
  slug         = "my-graph"
}

resource "grafbase_branch" "example" {
  account_slug = grafbase_graph.example.account_slug
  graph_slug   = grafbase_graph.example.slug
  name         = "feature-branch"
}
```

