## Environment Variables

The following environment variables can be used to configure the provider:

- `GRAFBASE_API_KEY` - API key for authentication with Grafbase. This can be used instead of the `api_key` provider argument.

## Authentication

The Grafbase provider requires an API key for authentication. You can obtain an API key from your Grafbase dashboard.

The API key can be provided in one of the following ways:

1. Set the `api_key` argument in the provider configuration
2. Set the `GRAFBASE_API_KEY` environment variable

```terraform
provider "grafbase" {
  api_key = "your-api-key-here"
}
```

Or using an environment variable:

```bash
export GRAFBASE_API_KEY="your-api-key-here"
```

```terraform
provider "grafbase" {
  # api_key will be read from GRAFBASE_API_KEY environment variable
}
```
